needed to rerun the mkfs command correctly

/opt/VRTS/bin/mkfs â€“F vxfs /dev/vx/rdsk/alnradarapp_sync/imail_sync

that will force the correct mkfs command to run

NOW TO DEPORT DISK GROUP

umount /imailsync

vxvol -g alnradarapp_sync stopall

vxdg deport alnradarapp_sync 

NOW IMPORT ON the OTHER NODE

vxdg import alnradarapp_sync 

vxvol -g alnradarapp_sync startall

vxvol -g alnradarapp_sync resync imail_sync

mount -F vxfs /dev/vx/dsk/alnradarapp_sync/imail_sync /imailsync
